{
  "stem": "14463.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Americans dropped the bombs on Nagasaki and Hiroshima, and they were frightened that the next load would be on Moscow, Leningrad, because they knew that they hate the communists, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was, straight away, after that mood of happiness and joy, there was a mood of fear.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, at that time, Russia didn't have the atom bomb yet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What did you decide to do with your mother at that stage?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that stage, we couldn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just stayed where we are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they came to us and they-- not came to us, but they announced, [INAUDIBLE], who-- and that is where our thoughts and [NON-ENGLISH] was right.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whoever is not a Russian citizen cannot stay in Russia and cannot stay in Kyzylorda, but you have to go and register and go back to where you come from.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's where we're justified not to take the Russian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it took awhile before-- the war finished in '45, and we were given permission to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not permission, but we were allocated room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was cattle trains again, you know, in '46.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you know the fate of the rest of your family at that stage?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the journey took us four weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, I was a cook level.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, there was a commandant there which was organizing, you know, food and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was his helper.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was wearing a pajama which my mother made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I was weaving it and my mother was sewing it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after I got married, I took it home, and the second or third day after my marriage my wife thought it was a piece of schmuk and so she threw it out.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
